videos.description: Tar Heels sophomore Armando Bacot gets the ball down low and rises up over a Charleston defender for a two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (North Carolina's Bacot throws down on defender) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: North Carolina's Bacot throws down on defender

videos.description: North Carolina guard R.J. Davis comes up with a steal on defense and then absorbs contact at the rim for the hoop and the harm.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Davis hustles for steal, and-1 bucket) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davis hustles for steal, and-1 bucket

videos.description: North Carolina guard Caleb Love drops to the floor to gain possession and then gives it up to R.J. Davis, who finishes with an easy layup in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Love dives to floor to earn Tar Heel a fast-break score) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Love dives to floor to earn Tar Heel a fast-break score

videos.description: Dontavius King knocks down a 3-pointer from the corner to give Charleston the lead over North Carolina for the first time.

videos.headline: King's triple gives Charleston lead over UNC

videos.description: North Carolina big man Armando Bacot blocks a shot on defense and then goes to work in the post on the other end for an and-1 basket.
